import React from 'react';
import styled from 'styled-components';

const LogoContainer = styled.div`
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: ${props => props.theme.spacing.sm};
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: ${props => props.theme.transitions.base};
  
  &:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }
`;

const LogoIcon = styled.div`
  width: ${props => props.size === 'large' ? '48px' : props.size === 'medium' ? '36px' : '28px'};
  height: ${props => props.size === 'large' ? '48px' : props.size === 'medium' ? '36px' : '28px'};
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
`;

const LogoText = styled.span`
  font-family: ${props => props.theme.fonts.primary};
  font-weight: ${props => props.theme.fontWeights.bold};
  font-size: ${props => props.size === 'large' ? props.theme.fontSizes['2xl'] : 
                        props.size === 'medium' ? props.theme.fontSizes.xl : 
                        props.theme.fontSizes.lg};
  background: ${props => props.theme.colors.gradientPrimary};
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
`;

const LokanexLogo = ({ size = 'medium', showText = true, ...props }) => {
  return (
    <LogoContainer {...props}>
      <LogoIcon size={size}>
        <svg
          width="100%"
          height="100%"
          viewBox="0 0 100 100"
          fill="none"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        >
          {/* Main diamond shape */}
          <polygon
            points="50,10 80,50 50,90 20,50"
            fill="url(#diamondGradient)"
            stroke="url(#diamondStroke)"
            strokeWidth="1"
          />
          
          {/* Inner rotated square */}
          <rect
            x="35"
            y="35"
            width="30"
            height="30"
            fill="url(#squareGradient)"
            stroke="url(#squareStroke)"
            strokeWidth="1"
            transform="rotate(45 50 50)"
          />
          
          {/* Central circle */}
          <circle
            cx="50"
            cy="50"
            r="8"
            fill="url(#centerGradient)"
          />
          
          {/* Corner elements */}
          <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="2" fill="url(#corner1)" />
          <circle cx="80" cy="20" r="2" fill="url(#corner2)" />
          <circle cx="20" cy="80" r="2" fill="url(#corner3)" />
          <circle cx="80" cy="80" r="2" fill="url(#corner4)" />
          
          {/* Side elements */}
          <rect x="5" y="47" width="8" height="6" fill="url(#side1)" rx="1" />
          <rect x="87" y="47" width="8" height="6" fill="url(#side2)" rx="1" />
          <rect x="47" y="5" width="6" height="8" fill="url(#side3)" rx="1" />
          <rect x="47" y="87" width="6" height="8" fill="url(#side4)" rx="1" />
          
          {/* Connection lines */}
          <line x1="20" y1="20" x2="35" y2="35" stroke="url(#conn1)" strokeWidth="1" opacity="0.5" />
          <line x1="80" y1="20" x2="65" y2="35" stroke="url(#conn2)" strokeWidth="1" opacity="0.5" />
          <line x1="20" y1="80" x2="35" y2="65" stroke="url(#conn3)" strokeWidth="1" opacity="0.5" />
          <line x1="80" y1="80" x2="65" y2="65" stroke="url(#conn4)" strokeWidth="1" opacity="0.5" />
          
          {/* Gradients */}
          <defs>
            <linearGradient id="diamondGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="50%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#0099cc" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="diamondStroke" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ffffff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#e0e0e0" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="squareGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ffffff" stopOpacity="0.8" />
              <stop offset="50%" stopColor="#00d4ff" stopOpacity="0.4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" stopOpacity="0.2" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="squareStroke" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
            </linearGradient>
            <radialGradient id="centerGradient" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ffffff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="corner1" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff8c42" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="corner2" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#44a08d" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="corner3" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#0099cc" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="corner4" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff8c42" />
            </radialGradient>
            <linearGradient id="side1" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#0099cc" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="side2" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#44a08d" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="side3" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff8c42" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="side4" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#0099cc" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="conn1" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="conn2" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="conn3" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="conn4" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
            </linearGradient>
          </defs>
        </svg>
      </LogoIcon>
      {showText && <LogoText size={size}>Lokanex</LogoText>}
    </LogoContainer>
  );
};

export default LokanexLogo;
